overview: Jesse Lawrence is CEO of TiqIQ, the leading event ticket aggregation platform and destination. He has 15 years of product and business development experience for growth-stage businesses, including Starmedia, The Wedding List and MediaMath, where he led 3rd party data partnerships and strategy.  He also spent 4 years at Updata Partners, a $500M venture capital firm. After Updata, Mr. Lawrence was Vice President at IAC (Nasdaq: IACI), where he helped launch three start-ups and manage business development and operations for Programming Group properties.
